{"tid":27532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人死左之後 身邊人係咪先會講真心話","createTime":"2016-12-07T11:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T14:29:27.000Z","uid":16454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3a3fdb17fff40955d33436042dd37876ca54df","tid":27532,"uid":16454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"如果你死左 有冇諗過身邊人會同你講啲咩野<br />\n如果你可以知道佢地係你死後會對你講咩 其實就算死左都幾値得 <br />\n<br />\n利申 冇自殺諗法嘅"},{"pid":"7f677a1795a4c5c626e2be5f04864a380e3badd8","tid":27532,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:31:00.000Z","msg":"死咗點聽真心話？"},{"pid":"3a5dc533accd926cedbc17e3285c772a15f1b01b","tid":27532,"uid":16454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死咗點聽真心話？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果可以係你靈魂出竅個刻睇到聽到啲人對我所講嘅野 咁我會即刻死 但我知係個一刻我都會後悔"},{"pid":"4e3bf50e3501682ad02a5bb64cf26f74803316ca","tid":27532,"uid":30638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"瀕死經驗係個唔錯嘅玩法，唔會死又聽到真心嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e8b52380a844f1ec1e9abf7caf451b3ec06a4b","tid":27532,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:29:27.000Z","msg":"無野係真心話,係咪悟得透要睇咩人"}]}